org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl

Class LegacyParserBridgeQueryTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl.LegacyParserBridgeQueryTranslator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryTranslator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FullTextSearchQueryTranslator, OgmQueryTranslator

    public abstract class LegacyParserBridgeQueryTranslator
extends Object
implements QueryTranslator
    A QueryTranslator which delegates most of the work to the existing JP-QL parser implementation. Specifically, all methods which only depend on the structure of the incoming JP-QL query are delegated. Only those methods depending on the translated query (such as QueryTranslator.list(org.hibernate.engine.spi.SessionImplementor, org.hibernate.engine.spi.QueryParameters) are handled by this class and its sub-classes. Over time, more and more methods should be implemented here rather than delegating them.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
